data.name: ReadFipsTribAddress
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, FAX_EXTENSION, FAX_AREA_CD, PHONE_EXTENSION, AREA_CD, TYPE, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, [STATE], ZIP_CD, ZIP4, ZIP3, COUNTY, STREET_3, STREET_4, PROVINCE, POSTAL_CODE, COUNTRY, PHONE_NUMBER, FAX_NUMBER, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TSTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPD_TSTAMP from CKT_FIPS_TRIB_ADDR where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: UpdateFipsTribAddress
data.value: update CKT_FIPS_TRIB_ADDR set FAX_EXTENSION = @faxExtension, FAX_AREA_CD = @faxAreaCd, PHONE_EXTENSION = @phoneExtension, AREA_CD = @areaCd, TYPE = @type, STREET_1 = @street1, STREET_2 = @street2, CITY = @city, [STATE] = @state, ZIP_CD = @zipCd, ZIP4 = @zip4, ZIP3 = @zip3, COUNTY = @county, STREET_3 = @street3, STREET_4 = @street4, PROVINCE = @province, POSTAL_CODE = @postalCode, COUNTRY = @country, PHONE_NUMBER = @phoneNumber, FAX_NUMBER = @faxNumber, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, LAST_UPD_TSTAMP = @lastUpdTstamp where IDENTIFIER = @identifier
